      "author": "liufree",
      "description": "## Documentation\r\n\r\n- Updated README (EN & ZH) with new feature descriptions:\r\n  - Local semantic cloze generation (no AI API required)\r\n  - Dual API format support (OpenAI-compatible & Anthropic)\r\n  - Stream rendering with real-time AI response display\r\n  - Multi-profile configuration with quick-switch toolbar",
      "downloadCount": 1,
      "draft": false,
