      "publishedAt": "2026-07-04T17:32:16Z",
      "tag": "1.3.1"
    },
    {
      "assets": [],
      "author": "liufree",
      "description": "## New Features\n\n### Local Semantic Cloze Generation\n- Added a \"Local (Semantic)\" provider — no AI API key required\n- Heuristic-based pattern matching automatically identifies cloze-worthy content: bold/highlighted text, quoted terms, book titles, numbers, dates, percentages, acronyms, proper nouns, definition subjects, and term-frequency analysis for key phrase extraction\n- Supports both Chinese and English content with difficulty-based density control\n\n### Multi-Profile Configuration\n- Save multiple AI configurations; different devices can select different profiles\n- Profile management in settings: save as new, update, rename, delete\n- Quick profile switching via toolbar dropdown (hidden on mobile)\n- New users get two default profiles: \"Local\" mode and \"AI\" mode\n\n### Settings UI\n- API configuration fields are automatically hidden when Local provider is selected\n- All AI config changes auto-sync to the active profile",
      "downloadCount": 0,
      "draft": false,
      "name": "1.3.0",
